text: == Events == * May 29 – Battle of Ctesiphon * June 26 – Battle of Samarra * Petra, capital of the Nabataeans, is damaged by an earthquake. * April 20 – The planet Venus occults the planet Jupiter. == Births == * Sulpicius Severus, Christian writer * Wu Di, emperor of the Liu Song Dynasty == Deaths == * Consort Zhou, concubine of Jin Chengdi * June 26 – Julian, Roman Emperor * Zhang Xuanjing, ruler of the Chinese state Former Liang Category:360s
